","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2757296194/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2757296194","tinyui":"/x/QgBZp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2757296194","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2757296194/Archived+Initiatives","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2757296194"}},{"id":"3063087149","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3063087149","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzA2MzA4NzE0OQ==","status":"current","title":"Facturación Electrónica","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":172688813},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3063087149/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3063087149/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3063087149/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3063087149/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3063087149","tinyui":"/x/LQCTtg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3063087149","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3063087149/Facturaci+n+Electr+nica","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3063087149"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"6de9be7e-3a77-4b39-8ab8-3142210093ff\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para la secci&oacute;n de carga de archivos dentro del flujo de Facturaci&oacute;n Electr&oacute;nica. </p><p>Vista Web: <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/q4Y1h3mLhjS3CeQU93p8Vw/%E2%9C%85-Onboarding-Portal-de-Comercios-2024?node-id=1187-20923&amp;t=2HXhJjVgVIDk1Uij-4\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://www.figma.com/design/q4Y1h3mLhjS3CeQU93p8Vw/%E2%9C%85-Onboarding-Portal-de-Comercios-2024?node-id=1187-20923&amp;t=2HXhJjVgVIDk1Uij-4</a></p><p>Vista Mobile: <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/q4Y1h3mLhjS3CeQU93p8Vw/%E2%9C%85-Onboarding-Portal-de-Comercios-2024?node-id=814-11685&amp;t=3wgLXTh5OAhwxPzG-4\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://www.figma.com/design/q4Y1h3mLhjS3CeQU93p8Vw/%E2%9C%85-Onboarding-Portal-de-Comercios-2024?node-id=814-11685&amp;t=3wgLXTh5OAhwxPzG-4</a> </p><p>Endpoint de la API de TaxIT para verificar constancia de usuario digital: <a href=\"https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/27482367/2sA3duFYJL#58394635-0bd6-4f74-934a-4c56e796ad04\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/27482367/2sA3duFYJL#58394635-0bd6-4f74-934a-4c56e796ad04</a> </p><p> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 395.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 111.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 253.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Servicio / Portal</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar el endpoint de get_company_attachments para que reciba el producto como par&aacute;metro opcional, y en el caso de ser Facturaci&oacute;n Electr&oacute;nica que pida los archivos de &ldquo;Contancia de DNIT&rdquo; y &ldquo;Formulario Definitivo&rdquo;</p><p><em>Agregar tambi&eacute;n links a youtube, por ende vamos a tener que agregar otra columna donde vamos a poner estos links.</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear pantalla de Carga de Archivos</p><p><em>Llamar endpoint de get_company_attachments</em></p><p><em>Web y Mobile</em></p><p><em>Cambio de componente seg&uacute;n si el archivo est&aacute; cargado o no</em></p><p><em>Mensajes de error</em></p><p><em>Vista del archivo Cargado</em></p><p><em>Redirecci&oacute;n a urls</em></p><p><em>Descarga de PDFs de ejemplo</em></p><p><em>Opci&oacute;n de borrado de archivo adjunto</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">24</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Llamar al endpoint de TaxIT para validar el archivo de &ldquo;Constancia de DNIT&rdquo; </p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Llamar al endpoint de TaxIT para validar el archivo de &ldquo;Timbrado Definitivo&rdquo; </p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Validar que el RUC / CI que devuelve TaxIT coincide con el registrado por el usuario en el flujo. </p><p><em>Si no coincide, mostrar mensaje de error</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Integraci&oacute;n con endpoint de TaxIT de &ldquo;Constancia de DNIT&rdquo; en external-services</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p>external-services</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Integraci&oacute;n con endpoint de TaxIT  de &ldquo;Timbrado Definitivo&rdquo; en external-services</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p>external-services</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Integraci&oacute;n con endpoint de TaxIT de &ldquo;Constancia de DNIT&rdquo; en commerce-service y guardar la respuestsa en la tabla de Leads  </p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Integraci&oacute;n con endpoint de TaxIT  de &ldquo;Timbrado Definitico&rdquo; en commerce-service y guardar la respuestsa en la tabla de Leads  </p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Validar que los archivos obligatorios est&eacute;n adjuntos al momento de avanzar </p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Enviar los archivos a commerce-service y guardarlos como adjuntos al C4C</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Integraci&oacute;n con el resto del flujo</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite </p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">110</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>126</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><ac:adf-extension><ac:adf-node type=\"panel\"><ac:adf-attribute key=\"panel-type\">note</ac:adf-attribute><ac:adf-content><p>Preguntas</p></ac:adf-content></ac:adf-node><ac:adf-fallback><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);border-color: rgb(153,141,217);border-width: 1.0px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);\">\n<p>Preguntas</p>\n</div></div></ac:adf-fallback></ac:adf-extension><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"df39bc32-2722-40c6-b433-4529f0480f16\"><tbody><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3263791105"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":6408},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3263791105/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3263791105/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3263791105/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3263791105/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3263791105","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3263791105/Carga+de+Archivos+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3263791105","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3263791105","tinyui":"/x/AYCJwg","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}